<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3147143" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".uno:UseWizards">Specifies whether to start the wizard automatically when inserting a new control.</ahelp> This setting applies globally to all documents.</paragraph>
